## Additional Terms for Government Use

This software is designed for use in government and public sector environments.
When deployed in such contexts, users should ensure compliance with:

- Government of Canada privacy and security requirements
- Treasury Board Secretariat digital standards
- Provincial and federal accessibility standards (WCAG 2.1 AA)
- Any applicable data protection and privacy legislation

